Q12. 
Write a short program that prints the numbers 1 to 10 using a for loop. Then write an equivalent program that prints the numbers 1 to 10 using a while loop.
Ans-
------using for loop------
for i in range(1,11):
       print(i)
----using while loop------    
i= 1
while i<11:
    print(i)
    i+=1
